Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:13.32,tanda-5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs100\bord0\shad0\pos(960,370)\c&HC4DAE2&}Sang Penguasa Keserakahan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:28.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seandainya butuh sesuatu selama di sini,\Njangan sungkan untuk menghubungi kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:40.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah dahulu ini kastel\NRaja Iblis Clayman, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:45.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru, apa reruntuhannya\Nada di dalam kastel ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pintu masuknya ada di luar kastel ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kastel Clayman itu dibangun\Ndi atas reruntuhan kuno Amrita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:59.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemandangannya bagus, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tidak sabar, ya, Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalannya sambil hadap\Nke depan, bahaya kalau...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:15.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah pintu menuju reruntuhan kuno,\Nkota bawah tanah Amrita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:17.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini reruntuhan kuno Amrita?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahulu, pernah ada sebuah kota di Amrita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekaisaran Sihir Agung Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:04.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Negara yang ada di masa lampau itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pernah mencapai puncak kejayaannya\Nsebagai surga para Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akibat perbuatan bodoh\Nyang dilakukan segelintir orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Kaisar Naga murka,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan surga itu pun berubah menjadi\Npuing-puing dalam semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, mereka yang dikutuk menjadi Dark Elf\Nakibat dosa menghancurkan negara,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:33.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mencari tanah baru demi melarikan diri\Ndari pandangan Putri Kaisar Naga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:37.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di antara mereka,\Naku yang dulu pun ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:43.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di tanah tempat kami melarikan diri itulah\Nkami membangun sebuah ibu kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar teknologi Elf tidak punah,\Nkami mengabadikan semuanya di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah awal mula terciptanya Amrita,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ibu kota dari Negara Boneka Jistave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:01.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang juga merupakan wujud asli\Ndari reruntuhan kuno Amrita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada reruntuhan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih mirip kota, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata masih ada yang tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku tidak menyangka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reruntuhan ini memiliki tiga tingkat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:54.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tingkat atas inilah yang kami gunakan\Nsebagai tempat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, mengingat ini di bawah tanah,\Ncahayanya datang dari mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini disinkronkan dengan pergerakan matahari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:09.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Sihir kuno di sini\Nmasih berfungsi sepenuhnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini saja sudah penemuan besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:18.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim, setelah penyelidikan selesai,\Nini akan menjadi wilayahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu bersedia membiarkan\Nmereka tetap tinggal di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, boleh saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Raja Iblis Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sungkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:37.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang penting kalian melaksanakan\Ntugas sebagai rakyatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pintu menuju lantai tengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kami bisa masuk\Nke tingkat yang lebih dalam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:58.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku dengar ada makam\Ndi lantai terbawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:04.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, hanya Tuan Clayman\Nyang bisa masuk ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lah, kalau tidak bisa dibuka,\Nbagaimana cara menyelidiki dalamnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih naif, Gobta.\NShion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan pada saya!\NSaya akan buka dengan satu tebasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mekanisme sihir kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:29.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibuka paksa,\Nsistem pertahanan kota akan aktif.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jebakan untuk penyusup, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung tidak ditebas tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:38.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian itu cuma perangkat kuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, masa jebakannya masih aktif?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya masih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buktinya, sihir cahaya tadi masih berfungsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, saatnya menganalisis pintu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rumus yang baru kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita gabungkan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, ayo kita coba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:06.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Clayman pernah ke lantai terbawah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:09.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia ada hubungannya\Ndengan reruntuhan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia belum lama berkuasa di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi hampir tidak mungkin terlibat\Ndengan reruntuhan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia berhasil\Nmemecahkan rumus sihir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:24.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seingatku dia raja iblis yang unggul\Ndalam hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:28.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kemampuan dia apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Skill Unik bernama "Manipulator".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:36.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuannya membaca urat bumi\Ndan mengendalikan alirannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, aku yang sudah melahap\Norang itu juga bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini akan jadi analisis yang panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah, kita lakukan dengan serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh perlihatkan padaku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumus sihirnya saling tumpang tindih\Nsehingga terlihat rumit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:06.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumus sihir di pintu ini\Nterbagi jadi tiga jenis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk mengunci pintu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:13.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengalirkan energi urat bumi\Nke seluruh dinding,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan jebakan untuk mencegah pintu\Nterbuka secara tidak sengaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jebakan ini yang agak merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aktif, aliran energi\Nurat bumi akan terputus,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan lampu di lantai ini akan padam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:30.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam kegelapan, semua energi akan dialihkan\Nuntuk membasmi penyusup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini rumus sihir yang paling baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kayaknya ada yang janggal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sendirian aku pasti bingung,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:49.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi berkat bantuan Guru Raphael,\Nini cuma seperti teka-teki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:54.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hapus bagian ini, lalu perbaiki rumusnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terpecahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya tinggal ulangi lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal ini tugas tim penyelidik,\Naku malah keasyikan sendiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang Anda suka begini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, kena sindir sama Gobta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, beliau bisa memecahkan\Nrumus sihir serumit ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:25.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, malah kelepasan.\NAku tidak bermaksud ikut campur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda ini bicara apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:31.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, siapa yang bisa menahan diri\Ndari memecahkan rumus seasyik ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:35.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh jelaskan pada kami cara Anda\Nmenganalisis ini, Raja Iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi pola ini yang menghalangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memang profesional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa ingin tahu mereka\Njauh lebih tinggi daripada harga diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru diberi sedikit petunjuk,\Nmereka langsung menguasai triknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua telah terpecahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita masuk, Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, tadinya aku mau langsung masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi matahari sudah mau tenggelam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita mulai besok saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata sistem ini benar-benar\Nterhubung dengan permukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:28.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana Milim?\NAda gerakan mencurigakan dari para penyelidik?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aman-aman saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:35.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Kagali?\NApa dia ada menghubungi seseorang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:40.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pakai pesan batin atau telepon sihir,\Npasti ketahuan olehku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:45.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti semua penyelidik bersih, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor.\NBelum bisa dipastikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalur komunikasi rahasia bisa dibuat\Nkalau terhubung lewat Lorong Jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti belum bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:58.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, mending hari ini tidur dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:02.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Aku tidak bisa tidur\Nmenunggu hari esok!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya mau piknik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berhasil, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba terasa lebih menekan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti dungeon di Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memeriksanya dengan Indra Sihir,\Ndan tempat ini seperti labirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:48.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin lantai tengah ini memang dirancang\Nsebagai penangkal penyusup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mural ini tampaknya menggambarkan\Nkehidupan pada masa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisinya masih bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini saja sudah bernilai seni tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat menyentuh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa melihat langsung\Nbukti peradaban kuno
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang biasanya hanya ada dalam dongeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kamu bilang begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:24.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi merasa nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:26.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:32.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim bangkit menjadi Raja Iblis\Nsetelah kematian naga kecil sahabatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi kami, ini hanya dongeng,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ini kenangan bagi Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pasti lapar, kan?\NAyo makan siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, waktunya makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan apinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal makan siangnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:05.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku meminta tetua Dark Elf\Nuntuk menyiapkan bekal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentar, supnya masih panas, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan daging kering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lezatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, makanan sebanyak ini\Ndisimpan di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku menyimpannya di perut,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}takutnya mereka salah paham\Ndan jadi tidak nafsu makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:29.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa sangka bisa makan yang selezat ini\Ndi dalam reruntuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku menghindari\Nmenggunakan api di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain demi keamanan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak mau warisan leluhur ini\Nkotor oleh asap hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:47.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bisa, aku ingin tetap melestarikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemikiran yang patut ditiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:14:00.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, kami memulai\Neksplorasi penuh di lantai tengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para penyelidik di sini benar-benar\Npunya rasa ingin tahu yang tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:10.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kujelaskan soal struktur labirin\Ndan trik penaklukan yang tren di dungeon kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka langsung menirunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat itu, pemetaan berjalan lancar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:19.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan lantai tengah berhasil\Ndilewati dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu pada hari ketiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:26.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami akhirnya tiba di depan pintu\Nmenuju lantai terbawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mekanismenya sama seperti di lantai tengah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi rumus sihirnya berkebalikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau terkena jebakan di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kita cari tahu pelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:41.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, bagaimana kalau rehat sejenak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya sampai lantai terbawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dilihat dari struktur rumus ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencoba tetap waspada,\Ntapi tidak ada yang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:56.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada yang mau menyerang,\Nseharusnya sekarang saatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:59.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin mereka hanya berani mengawasi\Nkarena ada Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan benaran melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu mencari cara lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:26.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persiapan untuk meredam kekuatan\NRaja Iblis Rimuru sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:38.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski telah disegel sejak zaman dulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:42.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata dia masih dipenuhi\Nkebencian yang mendalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gempa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, mengamuklah sepuasnya\Nmengikuti hasratmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Firasatku buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ada lonjakan energi raksasa\Nyang mengamuk di permukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:47.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terdeteksi penyusup di Amrita.\NLakukan pemusnahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sistem pertahanannya aktif sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor.\NMerasakan adanya reaksi permusuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang menyusup ke dalam reruntuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata mereka memang mengincar momen ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim, apa kamu merasakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rimuru, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada keperluan mendadak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:37.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor. Naga kuno bernama Chaos Dragon\Nyang pernah disegel Raja Iblis Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan pada kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak akan ada habisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, segera ke dalam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secepat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga mundur dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini lantai terbawah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mengejar kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya ke dalam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:46.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa sangka Chaos Dragon dipanggil di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:51.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Chaos Dragon?\NTiran itu muncul di zaman ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, Milim pergi untuk menghentikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:19:00.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi mengisolasiku, mereka bahkan berani\Nmemancing kemurkaan Milim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:04.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya mereka menghalalkan segala cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf jadi melibatkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata Anda banyak musuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku tidak ada niat bermusuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:18.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerajaan Falmuth, Raja Iblis Clayman,\Nsampai Orang Suci Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua yang menyerang duluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya membela diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisakah diselesaikan tanpa kekerasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa saja, asalkan\Nsalah satu pihak mau mengalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:33.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, mereka juga punya prinsipnya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak bisa mundur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya sudah melibatkan\Nrekan-rekan dari Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya sudah semua dikalahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, selama kita berupaya\Nmembangun hubungan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak perlu sampai bermusuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keserakahan manusia tidak ada batasnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:02.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keinginannya pun akan terus membesar\Nsetelah mengalahkan musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kita sepemikiran.\NAku Raja Iblis Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:13.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam kenal, Raja Iblis Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Maribel Rozzo, musuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musuh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku memastikan satu hal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:30.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunduklah padaku,\Nmaka pertempuran sia-sia ini bisa dihindari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kalimatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamulah yang harus tunduk padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paham kita tidak sejalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caramu hanya menyengsarakan rakyat kecil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi melindungi kekayaan segelintir elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaum lemah yang ditindas adalah hukum alam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monster pun hidup dengan hukum rimba, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:21:00.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku benci itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:04.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada orang yang selalu gagal dalam usahanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:08.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi nilai seseorang tidak bisa\Ndicampakkan begitu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setiap orang punya potensi tanpa batas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:17.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi caramu bahkan tidak memberi\Nmereka satu pun kesempatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:20.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah hal itu sangat disayangkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:25.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konyol.\NBenar-benar konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:31.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia terlahir dengan kesenjangan,\Ndan itu hal yang lumrah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:34.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang harus setara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:38.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya omong kosong anak kecil\Natau angan kaum tak berpunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa sangka seorang Raja Iblis\Nadalah pemimpi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kutunjukkan kenyataannya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil! Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:55.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Yuuki, Anda mengkhianati kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:02.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kita buktikan siapa yang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:03.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beralih ke mode tempur penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:17.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ketika semua manusia bisa saling memahami\Nmungkin tidak akan pernah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:23.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, justru itulah bukti\Ndari keberagaman umat manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:28.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk yang penuh kontradiksi\Ndalam proses evolusinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:34.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang paling benar\Nhanya bisa dibuktikan oleh pemenangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:09.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Sang Penguasa Keserakahan".
